This solution:

* Keeps APIs untouched âœ…
* Ensures no downtime or data loss âœ…
* Delivers seamless access to both hot and cold data âœ…
* Reduces long-term storage and RU/s costs âœ…
* Is easy to implement, automate, and maintain âœ…
